snippet.title: CHIN CHINNY CHIN MOUSE CHEESE CHIN TOES - PC Playthrough (Steam)
snippet.description:
Forget nuclear holocaust, forget rogue AI, in this insane universe the most catastrophic thing humanity will face is the sheer destructive power of a small mouse. But this is no ordinary mouse; CHIN CHINNY CHIN is hellbent on nibbling the toes of every last person on the planet. And that means the complete and utter annihilation of society as we know it.

Embark on a toe-tally awesome adventure as a relentless little mouse with a big appetite for nibbling toes. Explore a world spiraling into absurdity as you nibble your way through various states of societal collapse. Toe the line of hilarity and insanity!

CHIN CHINNY CHIN MOUSE CHEESE CHIN TOES (C) Revalopod
